reviewText: My twins are 4 and they've been wanting less Dora and more Wonder Pets and Blue's Clues.  However, I picked a Dora movie for them that night--Dora's Rescue in Mermaid Kingdom.  They loved it soooooo much!!  They keep asking to see it again, weeks later.  The music was less annoying than in most of the regular Dora Episodes.  I wish I had bought this movie instead of just renting it.
summary: I Wish I had Bought It
